relativistic species\ncan weaken the mass bounds for dark matter that couples to photons by up to an\norder of magnitude or more. Finally, we discuss the reach of the next\ngeneration of the CMB experiments in terms of probing the mass of the thermal\nrelic dark matter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Feb 2022 21:00:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Apr 2022 17:03:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-07"}
