ures from the shocked area in an extinction process are\nalso studied. Moreover, parametric studies considering various droplet\nconcentrations and cloud radii are performed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Feb 2022 06:39:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-09"}
