 tube at high currents. The\nnon-uniformity reveals an inhomogeneous distribution of strong-pinning centers\nacross large length scales in superconductors used for applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Feb 2022 11:02:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-09"}
